Symbol.Script_3D:
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL_3D_NONE then end
pen pen3D sect_fill gs_fill_type, gs_back_pen, gs_fill_pen, gs_cont_pen
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Hotspots ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if not(bNoHotspot) then hotspot -beamWidth/2, 0, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot beamWidth/2, 0, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot -beamWidth/2, beamThk, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot beamWidth/2, beamThk, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, beamThk/2, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1
hotspot -beamWidth/2, 0, beamHeight, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot beamWidth/2, 0, beamHeight, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot -beamWidth/2, beamThk, beamHeight, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot beamWidth/2, beamThk, beamHeight, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, beamThk/2, beamHeight, unID : unID = unID + 1
hotspot -beamWidth/2+overhang, 0, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot beamWidth/2-overhang, 0, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot -beamWidth/2+overhang, beamThk, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot beamWidth/2-overhang, beamThk, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Body ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if iBeamFamily = BEAM_FAMILY_UBLOCK_CONT_200 |\ iBeamFamily = BEAM_FAMILY_UBLOCK_CONT_250 |\ iBeamFamily = BEAM_FAMILY_UBLOCK_200 |\ iBeamFamily = BEAM_FAMILY_UBLOCK_250 \ then wb = 0.075 ws = 0.05 if iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_CONT_250_300 then ws = 0.055 if iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_CONT_250_365 then ws = 0.0625 if iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_400_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_425_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_480_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_200_300_600 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_200_300_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_300_600 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_300_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_200_365_600 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_200_365_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_365_600 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_365_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_200_400_600 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_200_400_500 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_400_600 |\ iBeam = BEAM_UBLOCK_250_400_500 \ then ws = 0.075 endif
put 0, 0, 15, beamThk, 0, 15, beamThk, beamHeight, 15, beamThk-ws, beamHeight, 15, beamThk-ws, wb, 15, ws, wb, 15, ws, beamHeight, 15, 0, beamHeight, 15, 0, 0, -1 else if iBeamFamily <> BEAM_FAMILY_NONE & iBeamFamily <> BEAM_FAMILY_CUSTOM then put 0, 0, 15, beamThk, 0, 15, beamThk, beamHeight, 15, 0, beamHeight, 15, 0, 0, -1 endif endif
if nsp then if iBeamType = BEAM_TYP_BLOCK then for i = 1 to n addx -beamWidth/2 + (i-1)*(groutWidth + brickWidthOne) roty 90 rotz 90 if i = n then prism_ nsp/3, brickWidthOne, get(nsp) else prism_ nsp/3, brickWidthOne, use(nsp) endif del 3 next i else addx -beamWidth/2 + BIGEPS/2 roty 90 rotz 90 prism_ nsp/3, beamWidth - BIGEPS, get(nsp) del 3 endif endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Warning ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if bOversized | bOverLapped then
rotx 90 addz 2*EPS
if bOversized then for i = 1 to 2 call "ks_quadro_sign" parameters A = 0.2, B = 0.2, iSignType = 1 addz -beamThk-5*EPS next i del 2 endif
if bOverLapped then addx bOversized * 0.20 for i = 1 to 2 call "ks_quadro_sign" parameters A = 0.1, B = 0.1, iSignType = 2 addz -beamThk-5*EPS next i del 3 endif
del 2 endif
! ============================================================================== ! end unID ! ! ==============================================================================
Symbol.Script_2D:
fill gs_fill_type pen gs_cont_pen
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Hotspots ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ hotspot2 -beamWidth/2, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 beamWidth/2, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 -beamWidth/2, beamThk, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 beamWidth/2, beamThk, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 0, beamThk/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
hotspot2 -beamWidth/2+overhang, beamThk/2, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 beamWidth/2-overhang, beamThk/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Drawing ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if iBeamType = BEAM_TYP_BLOCK then for i = 1 to n add2 -beamWidth/2 + brickWidthOne/2 + (i-1)*(groutWidth + brickWidthOne), 0 poly2_b 5, 1+2, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -brickWidthOne/2, 0, 1, brickWidthOne/2, 0, 1, brickWidthOne/2, beamThk, 1, -brickWidthOne/2, beamThk, 1, -brickWidthOne/2, 0, -1 del 1 next i else poly2_b 5, 1+2, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -beamWidth/2, 0, 1, beamWidth/2, 0, 1, beamWidth/2, beamThk, 1, -beamWidth/2, beamThk, 1, -beamWidth/2, 0, -1 endif
! ============================================================================== ! end unID ! ! ==============================================================================
